<s> Here is how to do it with what Amaya supports right now.  </s>
<s> For a selection: 1. Highlight it.  </s>
<s> 2. Open the Style menu and modify the style in one of the four options at the top.  </s>
<s> For an element: 1. Select text within the element.  </s>
<s> 2. Press F2 to select it.  </s>
<s> 3. Repeat until desired element is selected (look in status bar).  </s>
<s> 4. Do step 2 for a selection.  </s>
<s> To expand a style to an entire page (for all elements in a page or certain classes): 1. Follow the steps for an element.  </s>
<s> 2. Highlight the element.  </s>
<s> 3. Click Style  Create rule.  </s>
<s> 4. Type either the element name (to apply to elements) or a class name to apply to a certain class (begin with a period).  </s>
<s> To apply a premade class: Either 1. Select an element or selection.  </s>
<s> 2. Click Style  Apply classes.  </s>
<s> or 1. Select an element or selection.  </s>
<s> 2. Click Attributes  Class.  </s>
<s> 3. Type the appropriate class name.  </s>
